item.description:
@Darksterlin wrote:

Copy the following code and then go into class8.java and paste it there with the other item codes.

if(i == 16500)
{
class8.aStringArray189 = new String[5];
class8.aStringArray189[1] = “Wield”;
class8.aString170 = “Dragon claws”;
class8.aByteArray178 = “A set of fighting claws.”.getBytes();
class8.anInt174 = 13699;
class8.anInt181 = 630;
class8.anInt190 = 268;
class8.anInt198 = 1340;
class8.anInt204 = 0;
class8.anInt169 = -7;
class8.anInt194 = -13;
class8.anInt165 = 13698;
class8.anInt200 = 13698;
class8.anInt188 = -1;
class8.anInt164 = -1;
class8.anInt175 = -1;
class8.anInt197 = -1;
}

NEXT u wanna go to Client.java and look around till u find this:

if (playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 4587) // d scim
{
return 427;
}

once u find it u then wanna add the following right above it!

if (playerEquipment[playerWeapon] == 16500) // D claw
{
return 451;
}

Then save and compile it and then go to the server and type in “Add Model 42511” and “Add Model 42511”
and then restart it and waalah!
